<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Not Found — HIGE</title><link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Flex:opsz,wdth,wght@8..144,25..151,100..1000&family=Lora&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>body{background:#07090f;color:#a8bcdd;font-family:'Lora',serif;display:grid;place-items:center;
min-height:100vh;margin:0;text-align:center;padding:2rem}img{height:110px;margin-bottom:1.75rem;opacity:.7}
h1{font-family:'Roboto Flex',sans-serif;font-variation-settings:'wdth' 80,'opsz' 44,'wght' 1000;
font-size:clamp(2.5rem,7vw,4.5rem);color:#eef3ff;letter-spacing:-.04em;line-height:1;margin:0 0 .75rem}
p{max-width:420px;margin:0 auto 2rem;line-height:1.75}
a{display:inline-flex;gap:.5rem;background:#2563eb;color:#fff;padding:.8rem 1.8rem;border-radius:9px;
text-decoration:none;font-family:'Roboto Flex',sans-serif;font-variation-settings:'wdth' 78,'wght' 900;
font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}</style></head><body>
<div><img src="/img/hige-white.png" alt="HIGE">
<h1>Zone Not Found</h1>
<p>You have wandered somewhere that does not exist. Happens to the best of us &mdash; usually around 3am in Blackburrow.</p>
<a href="/">Back to Safety</a></div></body></html>